value.0: Like all drow, this woman is beautiful, but her features have a softness not usually found in her kind. Her eyes are deep wells of wisdom, hinting at both advanced age and limitless compassion.
A swirl of a vortex adorns the floor. Its meaning is not known to you.
Bound in leather, this tome looks well worn, and the writing on the cover has already started to fade.
